---
layout: text.njk
meta:
  title: Blog
  description: Here you can find answers to blogs about our creative & digital services. We understand that it can be hard to choose the right company to work with, so we have compiled a list of frequently asked questions to help you decide. If you have any other questions, please contact us.
pagination:
  data: collections.blogs
  size: 100
  alias: blogs
sitemap:
  changefreq: weekly
  priority: 0.7
---

<section class="container-sm mx-auto">
  <div class="mt-12 mb-12">
    <h1 class="text-13 text-weight-400 text-gradient">Blog</h1>
    <h2 class="text-5 text-charcoal-light text-weight-400">We've curated answers to the most common questions about our creative and digital services to guide your decision. For anything beyond, our team is here to provide clarity and insight.</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-12">
    {% for blog in blogs | reverse %}
      <a href="{{ blog.data.url }}" class="rounded-7">
        <article class="mb-10">
          {% set img =  "https://res.cloudinary.com/loopdash/image/upload/l_text:dm-sans-bold.ttf_40:" + (blog.data.title | urlencode) + ",co_rgb:584e46,g_south,y_-20,g_west,x_60/computer.png" %}
          <img src="{{ img }}" />
          <h3 class="text-6 text-weight-500 mb-2">{{ blog.data.title }}</h3>
          <div class="text-4 text-charcoal-light text-weight-400" id="content-{{ loop.index }}">
            {{ blog.data.meta.description | safe }}
          </div>
        </article>
        </a>
      </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
